{"tid":2261130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［RT] Tony Bobulinski: Jim Biden pitch客時 係撻埋佢身為joe顧問既身分","createTime":"2020-10-28T05:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T06:54:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f9ec300a4029871e4e22752a111b588230f7f380","tid":2261130,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tuckercarlson/status/1321263064319217665?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftuckercarlson%2Fstatus%2F1321263064319217665%3Fs%3D21&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7HlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=908ba0a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftuckercarlson%2Fstatus%2F1321263064319217665%3Fs%3D21&h=d51d4de1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tuckercarlson/status/1321263064319217665?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n間公司Hunter 同jim每人兩成<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R7eEWC2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR7eEWC2.png&h=f89d00c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEyeLwo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEyeLwo.png&h=1e43a743&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1a37c31b6a9446e48a27446096636f011c36dfa","tid":2261130,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"Wiki:<br />\n<br />\n合理推諉（Plausible deniability，也譯為似是而非的否認）是中央情報局（CIA）在20世紀60年代初創造的詞彙，用來描述高級官員隱瞞信息的情況，以便中央情報局非法或不受歡迎的活動，被公眾所知的情況下，保護他們免受影響。<br />\n<br />\n這個詞彙的根源可以追溯到1948年6月18日的哈里&middot;杜魯門國家安全委員會第10/2號文件，該文件將「秘密行動」定義為「&hellip;&hellip;本政府針對敵對的外國國家或團體進行或贊助的所有活動（除非另有說明），或支持友好的外國國家或團體但計劃和執行的任何活動，美國政府對此不承擔任何責任 對未經授權的人員來說很明顯，如果發現，美國政府可以合理地放棄對他們的任何責任。」[註 1][1]在艾森豪執政期間，NSC 10/2被納入更具體的NSC 5412/2「秘密行動」。[2]NSC 5412於1977年解密，並位於國家檔案館。[3]"},{"pid":"d8e1c7eb9d19a9914b747cf51b83720751048ebe","tid":2261130,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:50:20.000Z","msg":"另外<br />\n侵侵最新廣告：<br />\n曾經38次譴責白人優越主義<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/drgjackbrown/status/1319433028142202880?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdrgjackbrown%2Fstatus%2F1319433028142202880%3Fs%3D21&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7HlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=6b2b974d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdrgjackbrown%2Fstatus%2F1319433028142202880%3Fs%3D21&h=a71e2f43\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/drgjackbrown/status/1319433028142202880?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"5b4c0229d259c012d346423a11658c1d4a272c96","tid":2261130,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T06:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84f3cbbcfaf424e0fbeb77a4257cb3eebc443d8","tid":2261130,"uid":26708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T06:54:26.000Z","msg":"Ticker Carlson 全美no1 主持人"}]}